OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Disability campaigners are urging the  
OL,6, government to rethink its proposed     
OL,7, changes to social care funding.        
OL,9,FMPs are set to debate the Health and   
OL,10,FCare Bill, which includes plans to     
OL,11,Fexclude means-tested council support   
OL,12,Fpayments from a new #86,000 lifetime   
OL,13,Flimit on costs.                        
OL,15,FOne charity says making disabled people
OL,16,Fpay for their care is "morally unfair".
OL,18,FThe government says the plans strike a 
OL,19,Fbalance between people paying for their
OL,20,Fown needs, and help from the taxpayer. 
